# x_ tool index manifest
# Format: tool_name|description (one per line)
# Lines with "## Category" are section headers.
# Add new tools here when creating them.

## Core
x_backup|Tar backup: local or ssh (subcommands or menu)
x_guar_ghous|Ultimate disk nuke: Nix, Docker, caches, apt, node_modules (interactive)
x_backup_repos|Backup GitHub repos (mirror+tar), then archive or delete
x_crontab|Crontab manager: list, add, delete (subcommands or menu)
x_gradle_bootstrap|Gradle/Spring Boot wizard (-n NAME or interactive)
x_install|Add ~/.local/bin to PATH in shell config
x_mkdocs_init|MkDocs + GitHub Pages setup (interactive or -r/-o flags)
x_monokit|TypeScript monorepo CLI (init, add lib/app, switch deps)
x_monokit_menu|Interactive menu for x_monokit (options 5-7 need monokit-files)
x_nextjs_bootstrap|Next.js + Prisma + Shadcn + tRPC + Inngest (-n NAME or interactive)
x_phoenix_create|Create Phoenix app (-n NAME or interactive)
x_phoenix_enhance|Add Oban/auth/etc to existing Phoenix project
x_port|Port ops: list, query, kill, monitor (subcommands or menu)
x_ramdisk|tmpfs/RAM disk: create, list, unmount (subcommands or menu)
x_spring_init|Quick Spring Boot from start.spring.io (-n NAME or interactive)
x_ts_lib_create|TypeScript library scaffold (tsup, ESLint, Vitest)
x_tunnel|SSH tunnel: local/remote port forwarding
x_yt|YouTube/video downloader (yt-dlp or youtube-dl)

## Utilities
x_archive|Compress dir to tar.gz/zip (gz, bz2, xz, zst)
x_base64|Base64 encode/decode (stdin or file)
x_extract|Extract archives by extension (tar.gz, zip, 7z, etc.)
x_json|Pretty-print JSON (jq or python)
x_password|Generate random password (copies to clipboard if xclip)

## Docker
x_docker_clean|Prune images, containers, volumes (menu or subcommands)
x_docker_compose|Scaffold docker-compose (app + postgres + redis)
x_docker_run|Interactive docker run with common flags

## Git
x_git_amend_date|Amend commit dates (interactive or -d for non-interactive)
x_git_clean|Delete merged branches, prune remotes
x_git_repo_init|Create repo, add remote, push initial
x_git_submodule|Init, update, add submodules
x_git_worktree|Add/list/remove git worktrees

## SSH
x_ssh_config|Add host block to ~/.ssh/config
x_ssh_key|Generate SSH key, add to agent, copy to clipboard

## Python
x_py_project|Scaffold pyproject.toml + venv + src layout
x_py_venv|Create Python venv, optionally install deps

## Node
x_node_clean|Remove node_modules + lockfile, reinstall
x_node_version|Show Node/npm/pnpm, suggest fnm/nvm if missing

## Certs
x_cert_check|Check SSL cert expiry and SANs for domain
x_cert_self|Generate self-signed cert for local dev

## Project bootstrap
x_go_init|Go mod init + cmd/main.go scaffold
x_rust_init|Cargo init, optional --deps (serde, tokio, etc.)
